data.description: This is a beautiful, well cared for home,  It has a nice covered porch on front  & large deck on back.  It has the spacious living room, dining room & kitchen open.  Lots of  pretty cabinets in kitchen.  Huge master bedroom, bath, & walk-in closet.  All 3 bedrooms have walk-in closets.This home is near the end of the road, has a concrete drive, large storage building, & partially fenced-in back yard.This home is minutes from golf course, public boat docks, & Norris Lake.Approximately 45 minutes to Knoxville.
